ent-crashes-car-into-sleeping-footpath-dwellers-5910190%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fnagpur-news%2F2-dead-after-drunk-nagpur-student-crashes-car-into-sleeping-footpath-dwellers-5910190%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fnagpur-news%2F2-dead-after-drunk-nagpur-student-crashes-car-into-sleeping-footpath-dwellers-5910190%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BEven%20If%200.001%25%20Negligence...%26quot%3B%3A%20Top%20Court%20Blasts%20Exam%20Body%20NTA%20In%20NEET%20Row%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmid%20concerns%20about%20the%20National%20Eligibility-cum-Entrance%20Test%20(NEET)%20for%20admission%20into%20medical%20colleges%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20came%20down%20heavily%20on%20the%20National%20Testing%20Agency%20(NTA)%2C%20which%20conducts%20the%20nationwide%20exam%20for%20medical%20college%20aspirants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20there's%20even%200.001%25%20negligence%20on%20anyone's%20part%2C%20it%20should%20be%20thoroughly%20dealt%20with%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20-%20while%20hearing%20a%20batch%20of%20petitions%20over%20the%20alleged%20irregularities%20in%20the%20exam%20-%20said%20it%20expects%20a%20%26quot%3Btimely%20action%26quot%3B%20from%20the%20NTA%20and%20that%20the%20agency%20must%20ensure%20that%20all%20candidates%20are%20treated%20fairly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20an%20agency%20which%20is%20conducting%20the%20examination%2C%20you%20must%20act%20fair.%20If%20there%20is%20a%20mistake%2C%20say%20yes%2C%20this%20is%20a%20mistake%2C%20and%20this%20is%20the%20action%20we%20are%20going%20to%20take.%20At%20least%20that%20inspires%20confidence%20in%20your%20performance%2C%26quot%3B%C2%A0a%20bench%20of%20Justice%20Vikram%20Nath%20and%20Justice%20SVN%20Bhatti%20told%20the%20NTA.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20also%20observed%20that%20the%20agency%20shouldn