0the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20the%20Assembly%20polls%20held%20alongside.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EJust%20as%20justice%20should%20not%20only%20be%20served%2C%20but%20should%20also%20appear%20to%20have%20been%20served%2C%20so%20should%20democracy%20not%20only%20prevail%20but%20must%20appear%20to%20be%20prevalent%20undoubtedly.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnIn%20electoral%20practices%20across%20the%20world%20in%20almost%20every%20advanced%20democracy%2C%20paper%20ballots%20are%20used%2C%20not%20EVMs.%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20YS%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy%20(%40ysjagan)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fysjagan%2Fstatus%2F1802892290257789049%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJune%2018%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20as%20justice%20should%20not%20only%20be%20served%2C%20but%20should%20also%20appear%20to%20have%20been%20served%2C%20so%20should%20democracy%20not%20only%20prevail%20but%20must%20appear%20to%20be%20prevalent%20undoubtedly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20electoral%20practices%20across%20the%20world%20in%20almost%20every%20advanced%20democracy%2C%20paper%20ballots%20are%20used%2C%20not%20EVMs.%20We%20too%20must%20move%20towards%20the%20same%20in%20upholding%20the%20true%20spirit%20of%20our%20democracy%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Reddy%20posted%20on%20X%20this%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20YSR%20Congress%20chief's%20remark%20is%20significant%20as%20it%20joins%20cause%20with%20leaders%20of%20the%20INDIA%20Opposition%20bloc%2C%20who%20have%20been%20flagging%20apprehensions%20that%20EVMs%20can%20be%20manipulated.%20The%20Election%20Commission%20has%20trashed%20such%20arguments%20and%20stressed%20that%20robust%20safeguards%20make%20EVMs%20the%20most%20reliable%20voting%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%20five%20years%2C%20the%20YSRCP%2C%20though%20not%20part%20of%20either%20NDA%20or%20UPA%2C%20extended%20critical%20support%20to%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20on%20key%20legislation.%20But%20in%20this%20election%2C%20the%20BJP%20allied%20with%20its%20arch-rival%2C%20N%20Chandrababu-led%20TDP%2C%20and%20the%20NDA%20bloc%20swept%20the%20polls%20in%20Andhra.%20The%20NDA%20alliance%20won%20164%20out%20of%20175%20seats%20in%20Assembly%20polls%2C%20reducing%20YSRCP%20score%20to%20just%2011.%20Of%20the%2025%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20the%20state%2C%20NDA%20won%2021%20and%20the%20YSRCP%20four.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgainst%20this%20backdrop%2C%20Jagan%20Reddy's%20post%20hints%20at%20a%20political%20realignment%20that%20may%20compound%20troubles%20for%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20in%20Parliament%2C%20especially%20now%20that%20it%20does%20not%20have%20a%20clear%20majority%20and%20needs%20its%20NDA%20partners%20to%20stay%20on%20in%20power.%20The%20YSRCP%20now%20has%20four%20MPs%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%2011%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20media%20interaction%2C%20YSRCP%20leader%20V%20Vijayasai%20Reddy%20said%20his%20party%20may%20have%20lost%20power%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20but%20not%20its%20strength%20in%20the%20Upper%20House.%20%26quot%3BPlease%20remember%20that%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20central%20government%20needs%20our%20support%20to%20pass%20bills%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20There%20should%20be%20no%20doubt.%20We%20are%20as%20strong%20as%20the%20TDP%20even%20though%20we%20have%20lost%20power%20in%20the%20state.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Reddy%2C%20however%2C%20indicated%20that%20his%20party%20is%20open%20to%20extending%20issue-based%20support%20to%20the%20NDA%20government%20if%20the%20matter%20is%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20country%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Is%20The%20EVM%20Row%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20debate%20over%20the%20reliability%20of%20EVMs%20has%20revived%20weeks%20after%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20poll%20results%2C%20thanks%20to%20a%20remark%20by%20'X'%20boss%20and%20Tesla%20CEO%20Elon%20Musk.%20Responding%20to%20a%20post%20on%20poll%20regularities%20in%20Puerto%20Rico.%20Flagging%20manipulation%20risks%20in%20EVMs%2C%20Musk%20tweeted%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20should%20eliminate%20electronic%20voting%20machines.%20The%20risk%20of%20being%20hacked%20by%20humans%20or%20AI%2C%20while%20small%2C%20is%20still%20too%20high.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20remark%20opened%20the%20floodgates.%20Shortly%20after%2C%20BJP%20leader%20and%20former%20Union%20minister%20Rajeev%20Chandrashekar%20said%20Musk's%20remark%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bhuge%20sweeping%20generalization%20statement%20that%20implies%20no%20one%20can%20build%20secure%20digital%20hardware%26quot%3B.%20The%20BJP%20leader%20said%20that%20while%20the%20Tesla%20CEO's%20view%20may%20apply%20to%20other%20places%2C%20Indian%20EVMs%20are%20%26quot%3Bcustom%20designed%2C%20secure%20and%20isolated%20from%20any%20network%20or%20media%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bthere%20is%20no%20way%20in%26quot%3B.%20The%20minister%20also%20offered%20Musk%20a%20tutorial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElon%20Musk%2C%20however%2C%20double%20down.%20%26quot%3BAnything%20can%20be%20hacked%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Mr%20Chandrasekhar%20stuck%20to%20his%20guns%20and%20argued%20that%20while%20%26quot%3Banything%20is%20possible%26quot%3B%2C%20EVMs%20continue%20to%20be%20a%20reliable%20voting%20method%20as%20compared%20to%20paper%20ballots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpposition%20leaders%20latched%20on%20to%20Musk's%20remarks%20and%20questioned%20the%20reliability%20of%20EVMs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20said%20EVMs%20in%20Indian%20%26quot%3Bare%20a%20'black%20box'%20and%20nobody%20is%20allowed%20to%20scrutinize%20them%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkhilesh%20Yadav%2C%20Samajwadi%20Party%20chief%20and%20a%20Congress%20ally%2C%20shared%20Musk's%20post.%20%26quot%3BTechnology%20is%20to%20remove%20problems%2C%20if%20they%20become%20a%20cause%20of%20problems%2C%20their%20use%20must%20be%20stopped.%20When%20risks%20of%20EVM%20tampering%20are%20being%20flagged%20in%20several%20elections%20across%20the%20world%20and%20well-known%20technology%20experts%20are%20flagging%20risks%2C%20the%20BJP%20must%20clear%20the%20air%20on%20why%20they%20are%20bent%20on%20using%20EVMs%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20demanding%20that%20upcoming%20polls%20be%20conducted%20by%20ballot%20paper%20method.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20maintains%20that%20the%20EVM%20voting%20method%20has%20robust%20technical%20and%20administrative%20safeguards%20in%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20media%20after%20the%20general%20election%20resuls%2C%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%20Rajiv%20Kumar%20took%20a%20swipe%20at%20those%20questioning%20EVMs.%20%26quot%3BWhy%20to%20accuse%20that%20poor%20fellow%3F%20Let%20it%20rest%20for%20a%20few%20days.%20Let%20EVM%20rest%20till%20the%20next%20election.%20Then%20it%20will%20come%20out%2C%20then%20its%20battery%20will%20be%20changed%2C%20then%20its%20papers%20will%20be%20changed.%20Then%20it%20will%20get%20abused%20again%2C%20but%20will%20deliver%20good%20results.%20It%20has%20been%20showing%20similar%20results%20since%20the%20last%2020-22%20elections%2C%20the%20government%20keeps%20changing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718692920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-12%2F7mhanj8k_jagan-reddy-650_625x300_31_December_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjagan-mohan-reddy-2024-election-results-weeks-after-andhra-rout-jagan-reddy-backs-ballot-voting-in-evm-debate-5914087%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20the%20raging%20debate%20over%20Electronic%20Voting%20Machines%20(EVM)%2C%20YSR%20Congress%20Party%20president%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy%20has%20called%20for%20a%20move%20towards%20voting%20by%20paper%20ballots.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%