693479243%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJune%2017%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20her%20entry%20into%20active%20politics%20in%202019%2C%20Priyanka%2C%2052%2C%20has%20been%20seen%20as%20a%20potential%20challenger%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20particularly%20from%20Varanasi%2C%20and%20as%20a%20successor%20to%20Congress%20veteran%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20in%20Rae%20Bareli.%20However%2C%20the%20Congress%20party%20has%20now%20decided%20to%20field%20her%20from%20Kerala's%20Wayanad.%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20recently%20decided%20to%20vacate%20the%20Wayanad%20seat%20for%20Priyanka%20while%20retaining%20Rae%20Bareli%2C%20has%20expressed%20confidence%20in%20her%20abilities%20to%20carry%20forward%20his%20legacy%20in%20Kerala.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20very%20happy%20to%20be%20able%20to%20represent%20Wayanad.%20All%20I'll%20say%20is%20that%20I%20won't%20let%20them%20feel%20his%20(Rahul's)%20absence.%20I%20will%20work%20hard%20and%20try%20my%20best%20to%20make%20everybody%20happy%20and%20be%20a%20good%20representative%2C%26quot%3B%20Priyanka%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20candidacy%20is%20seen%20as%20a%20strategic%20move%20by%20the%20Congress%20to%20strengthen%20its%20position%20in%20a%20state%20where%20the%20party%20has%20performed%20well%20in%20recent%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPriyanka's%20political%20journey%20has%20been%20marked%20by%20her%20roles%20as%20the%20general%20secretary%20in-charge%20of%20eastern%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20later%20the%20entire%20state.%20Despite%20mixed%20results%20in%20the%202019%20polls%2C%20she%20continued%20to%20bolster%20the%20party's%20grassroots%20presence.%20By%20December%202023%2C%20she%20had%20become%20the%20Congress'%20key%20strategist%20and%20star%20campaigner%20for%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20contributing%20significantly%20to%20the%20party's%20improved%20performance%2C%20which%20saw%20it%20secure%2099%20seats%2C%20up%20from%2052%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3