2%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Congress%20Campaigner%20For%202%20Decades%2C%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Takes%20Poll%20Dive%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress's%20decision%20to%20field%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20for%20the%20bye-election%20in%20Kerala's%20Wayanad%20marks%20her%20debut%20in%20electoral%20politics%2C%20but%20she%20has%20been%20part%20of%20the%20party's%20campaigns%20and%20outreach%20programmes%20for%20about%20two%20decades%20now.%20Her%20political%20journey%20has%20seen%20her%20grow%20from%20a%20campaign%20face%20to%20a%20party%20organiser%20who%20works%20on%20strategy%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20holds%20a%20Bachelor's%20degree%20in%20Psychology%20and%20a%20Master's%20in%20Buddhist%20studies.%20She%20is%20married%20to%20businessman%20Robert%20Vadra%20and%20has%20two%20children%20--%20son%20Raihan%20and%20daughter%20Miraya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20younger%20Gandhi%20sibling%2C%20often%20compared%20to%20her%20grandmother%20and%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Indira%20Gandhi%20for%20her%20looks%20as%20well%20as%20her%20taste%20for%20handloom%20sarees%2C%20took%20her%20first%20step%20into%20politics%20in%20the%202004%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20that%20marked%20her%20brother%20Rahul's%20electoral%20debut.%20Ahead%20of%20the%20general%20election%20that%20year%2C%20she%20campaigned%20for%20Rahul%20in%20Amethi%20and%20mother%20Sonia%20in%20Raebareli.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20many%20had%20expected%20that%20it%20would%20be%20the%20more%20charismatic%20and%20articulate%20Priyanka%20who%C2%A0would%C2%A0take%20the%20political%20plunge%20before%20Rahul.%C2%A0While%20Rahul%20was%20seen%20to%20be%20a%20reluctant%20politician%2C%20many%20believed%20Priyanka%20was%20the%20true%20representative%20of%20the%20Nehru-Gandhi%20family's%20political%20legacy.%C2%A0But%20in%20the%202004%20polls%2C%20she%20remained%20on%20the%20sidelines.%20A%20reason%20cited%20by%20many%20is%20that%20she%20wanted%20to%20focus%20on%20her%20toddlers%20first%20before%20joining%20politics%20full-time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20her%20role%20in%20the%20Congress%20expanded%2C%20albeit%20slowly.%20In%20the%202007%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20elections%2C%20she%20focused%20on%20interacting%20with%20local%20leaders%20and%20tackling%20infighting%20in%20the%20Assembly%20segments%20under%20Amethi%20and%20Raebareli%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats.%20The%20Congress%20won%2022%20Assembly%20seats%20that%20year%2C%20three%20less%20than%202002.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20next%20decade%2C%20she%20would%20largely%20appear%20only%20during%20elections%20and%20campaign%20for%20the%20Congress%20in%20family%20strongholds.%202019%20marked%20her%20formal%20entry%20into%20politics%20as%20the%20Congress%20appointed%20her%20general%20secretary%20in%20charge%20of%20eastern%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20country's%20most%20politically-significant%20state.%20The%20next%20year%2C%20she%20was%20named%20the%20in-charge%20of%20the%20whole%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20burst%20into%20political%20limelight%20during%20the%20Congress's%20protest%20over%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri%20incident%20in%20which%20a%20car%20allegedly%20driven%20by%20BJP%20leader%20Ajay%20Mishra%20Teni's%20son%20ran%20farmers%20over.%20She%20was%20first%20placed%20under%20house%20arrest%2C%20but%20she%20managed%20to%20evade%20the%20cops%20and%20proceed%20towards%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri.%20She%20was%20later%20taken%20into%20custody.%20The%20visuals%20of%20Ms%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20facing%20off%20with%20cops%20catapulted%20her%20from%20being%20a%20campaign%20face%20to%20a%20full-fledged%20politician%20who%20hits%20the%20streets%20and%20doesn't%20back%20off%20in%20the%20face%20of%20state%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202022%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20election%20was%20the%20first%20big%20campaign%20she%20led.%20The%20Congress%20fought%20solo%20and%20its%20manifesto%20focused%20on%20youth%20and%20women%20empowerment.%20Ms%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20led%20the%20fight%20with%20the%20slogan%2C%20Ladki%20Hoon%20Lad%20Sakti%20Hoon%2C%20aimed%20as%20an%20outreach%20to%20women%20voters.%20The%20efforts%2C%20however%2C%20did%20not%20pay%20off%20and%20the%20Congress%20won%20just%20two%20seats%20after%20contesting%20399%20--%205%20less%20than%20its%202017%20tally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20rout%20was%20a%20reality%20check%20for%20the%20Congress%20about%20its%20dwindling%20strength%20in%20the%20key%20state.%20Addressing%20party%20workers%20after%20the%20election%2C%20Ms%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20asked%20them%20to%20step%20up%20their%20efforts%20to%20connect%20with%20the%20people%20and%20stressed%20that%20poll%20promises%20have%20no%20impact%20unless%20the%20party%20expanded%20its%20outreach%20at%20the%20grassroots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20party%20rejig%20in%20December%202023%2C%20Ms%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20remained%20a%20Congress%20general%20secretary%2C%20but%20did%20not%20hold%20UP's%20charge.%20Her%20next%20big%20test%20was%20this%20year's%20general%20election.%20In%20these%20polls%2C%20which%20saw%20the%20Congress%C2%A0bounce%20back%C2%A0from%20its%202019%20score%20of%2052%20to%20winning%2099%20seats%2C%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20taking%20on%20the%20BJP%20and%20fine-tuning%20the%20party's%20strategies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20countering%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20charge%20on%20'mangalsutra'%20to%20camping%20in%20family%20strongholds%20Amethi%20and%20Raebareli%2C%20she%20was%20hands-on%20and%20among%20the%20Congress's%20most%20visible%20faces%20in%20its%20Lok%20Sabha%20poll%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20accused%20the%20Congress%20of%20preparing%20a%20wealth%20distribution%20plan%20under%20which%20women%20would%20lose%20their%20mangalsutra%2C%20Ms%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20came%20up%20with%20an%20emotional%20and%20spirited%20response%20--%20she%20said%20her%20grandmother%20Indira%20Gandhi%20had%20donated%20her%20mangalsutra%20to%20India's%20war%20fund%20and%20her%20mother%20Sonia%20sacrificed%20hers%20for%20this%20country%20when%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20was%20assassinated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20especially%20Amethi%20and%20Raebareli%2C%20she%20steered%20the%20Congress%20campaign%20as%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20travelled%20across%20the%20country%20for%20rallies.%20The%20results%20were%20impressive.%20The%20Congress%20won%20both%20strongholds%2C%20with%20Gandhi%20family%20loyalist%20KL%20Sharma%20pulling%20off%20a%20stunning%20win%20over%20BJP's%20Smriti%20Irani%20in%20Amethi.%20The%20Congress%20won%206%20seats%20in%20UP.%20Ms%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20was%20also%20the%20party's%20voice%20in%20multiple%20TV%20interviews%20in%20which%20she%20countered%20the%20BJP's%20attacks%20and%20articulated%20her%20party's%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20deciding%20to%20vacate%20the%20Wayanad%20seat%20and%20the%20Congress%20fielding%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20from%20there%2C%20the%20Parliament%20may%20just%20get%20another%20charismatic%20leader%20who%20will%20make%20the%20Opposition's%20arguments%20more%20forceful.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718687760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fp9bm781o_pgv_625x300_18_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpriyanka-gandhi-vadra-campaigner-to-strategist-to-candidate-priyanka-gandhis-political-journey-5913756%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Congress's%20decision%20to%20field%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20for%20the%20by-election%20in%20Kerala's%20Wayanad%20marks%20her%20debut%20in%20electoral%20politics%2C%20but%20she%20has%20been%20part%20of%20the%20party's%20campaigns%20and%20outreach%20programmes%20for%20about%20two%20decades%20now%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpriyanka-gandhi-vadra-campaigner-to-strategist-to-candidate-priyanka-gandhis-political-journey-5913756%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.amppro