0to%20services%20in%20US%20states%20where%20it%20is%20banned.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnMr%20Mallya%20was%20born%20in%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20California%2C%20and%20spent%20his%20childhood%20in%20England%20and%20the%20UAE.%20His%20father%2C%20Vijay%20Mallya%2C%20was%20the%20chairman%20of%20the%20UB%20Group%20and%20the%20owner%20of%20the%20now-defunct%20Kingfisher%20Airlines.%20Mr%20Mallya%20studied%20at%20Wellington%20College%20and%20Queen%20Mary%20University%20of%20London.%20Later%2C%20he%20attended%20the%20Royal%20Central%20School%20of%20Speech%20and%20Drama%2C%20launching%20his%20career%20in%20modelling%20and%20acting.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718687700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fhns3fq5_jasmine-sidhartha-mallya_625x300_18_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fsidhartha-mallya-to-get-married-this-week-who-is-his-fiancee-jasmine-5913695%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jasmine%20and%20Sidhartha%20Mallya%20got%20engaged%20in%20October%202023.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fsidhartha-mallya-to-get-married-this-week-who-is-his-fiancee-jasmine-5913695%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fsidhartha-mallya-to-get-married-this-week-who-is-his-fiancee-jasmine-5913695%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fsidhartha-mallya-to-get-married-this-week-who-is-his-fiancee-jasmine-5913695%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Top%20US%20Doctor%20Calls%20For%20%26quot%3BWarning%20Labels%26quot%3B%20On%20Social%20Media.%20Here's%20Why%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUS%20Surgeon%20General%20Vivek%20Murthy%20on%20Monday%20called%20for%20a%20warning%20label%20to%20be%20added%20to%20social%20media%20apps%20as%20a%20reminder%20that%20those%20platforms%20have%20caused%20harm%20to%20young%20people%2C%20especially%20adolescents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Murthy%20wrote%20in%20the%20New%20York%20Times%20on%20Monday%20that%20a%20warning%20label%20alone%20will%20not%20make%20social%20media%20safe%20for%20young%20people%20but%20that%20it%20can%20increase%20awareness%20and%20change%20behavior%20as%20shown%20in%20evidence%20from%20tobacco%20studies.%20The%20US%20Congress%20would%20need%20to%20pass%20legislation%20requiring%20such%20a%20warning%20label.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWHY%20IT%20IS%20IMPORTANT%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20long%20time%2C%20Mr%20Murthy%20has%20been%20warning%20that%20social%20media%20can%20profoundly%20harm%20the%20mental%20health%20of%20youth%2C%20particularly%20adolescent%20girls.%20In%20an%20advisory%20last%20year%2C%20he%20called%20for%20safeguards%20from%20tech%20companies%20for%20children%20who%20are%20at%20critical%20stages%20of%20brain%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%202019%20American%20Medical%20Association%20study%20showed%20that%20the%20risk%20of%20depression%20doubled%20for%20teenagers%20who%20were%20spending%20three%20hours%20a%20day%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKEY%20QUOTES%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20time%20to%20require%20a%20surgeon%20general's%20warning%20label%20on%20social%20media%20platforms%2C%20stating%20that%20social%20media%20is%20associated%20with%20significant%20mental%20health%20harms%20for%20adolescents%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Murthy%20wrote%20on%20Monday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20surgeon%20general's%20warning%20label%2C%20which%20requires%20congressional%20action%2C%20would%20regularly%20remind%20parents%20and%20adolescents%20that%20social%20media%20has%20not%20been%20proved%20safe%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECONTEXT%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20US%20states%20have%20been%20working%20to%20pass%20legislation%20to%20safeguard%20children%20from%20the%20harmful%20effects%20of%20social%20media%2C%20such%20as%20anxiety%2C%20depression%20and%20other%20mental%20illnesses%20as%20a%20result.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENew%20York%20state%20lawmakers%20this%20month%20passed%20legislation%20to%20bar%20social%20media%20platforms%20from%20exposing%20%26quot%3Baddictive%26quot%3B%20algorithmic%20content%20to%20users%20under%20age%2018%20without%20parental%20consent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20March%2C%20Florida%20Governor%20Ron%20DeSantis%20signed%20a%20bill%20that%20bans%20children%20under%2014%20from%20social%20media%20platforms%20and%20requires%2014-%20and%2015-year-olds%20to%20get%20parental%20consent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718687520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F0kfkf7no_vivek-murthy-_625x300_18_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftop-us-doctor-calls-for-warning-labels-on-social-media-heres-why-5913862%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22US%20Surgeon%20General%20Vivek%20Murthy%20on%20Monday%20called%20for%20a%20warning%20label%20to%20be%20added%20to%20social%20media%20apps%20as%20a%20reminder%20that%20those%20platforms%20have%20caused%20harm%20to%20young%20people%2C%20especially%20adolescents.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftop-us-doctor-calls-for-warning-labels-on-social-media-heres-why-5913862%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftop-us-doctor-calls-for-warning-labels-on-social-media-heres-why-5913862%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftop-us-doctor-calls-for-warning-labels-on-social-media-heres-why-5913862%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Human%20Error%20Or%20Signal%20Failure%3F%20What%20Led%20To%20Bengal%20Train%20Crash%20That%20Killed%209%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Kanchanjunga%20Express%20was%20travelling%20from%20Agartala%20in%20Tripura%20to%20Sealdah%20in%20Kolkata%20when%20a%20goods%20train%20hit%20it%20from%20behind%20near%20Rangapani%20station%2C%20close%20to%20New%20Jalpaiguri%20Monday%20morning%2C%20resulting%20in%20the%20deaths%20of%20nine%20people%20and%20injuries%20to%2041.%20Preliminary%20findings%20point%20to%20a%20combination%20of%20human%20error%20and%20signal%20failure%20as%20contributing%20factors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Railway%20Board's%20initial%20report%20on%20Monday%20revealed%20that%20the%20goods%20train%2C%20operating%20under%20a%20defective%20automatic%20signalling%20system%2C%20was%20travelling%20above%20speed%20limits%20when%20it%20crashed%20into%20the%20Kanchanjunga%20Express.%20The%20railways%20have%20not%20commented%20on%20this%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20automated%20system%20fails%2C%20railway%20protocol%20mandates%20a%20written%20authority%20known%20as%20TA%20912.%20This%20document%20authorises%20train%20drivers%20to%20pass%20all%20red%20signals%20due%20to%20the%20signalling%20defect%2C%20provided%20they%20adhere%20to%20stringent%20safety%20measures.%20Both%20the%20Kanchanjunga%20Express%20and%20the%20goods%20train%20had%20been%20issued%20TA%20912%20(pictured%20below).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fu67r2lrg_ta912_625x300_18_June_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20railway%20procedures%2C%20under%20TA%20912%2C%20drivers%20must%20stop%20for%20one%20minute%20at%20each%20defective%20signal%20and%20proceed%20at%20a%20maximum%20speed%20of%2010%20kmph.%20Additionally%2C%20they%20must%20maintain%20a%20150-metre%20gap%20from%20the%20preceding%20train%20to%20ensure%20adequate%20stopping%20distance%20if%20the%20previous%20train%20has%20not%20cleared%20the%20signal.%20However%2C%20in%20this%20incident%2C%20the%20goods%20train%20driver%20violated%20these%20critical%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kanchanjunga%20Express%20had%20cleared%20nine%20automatic%20signals%20with%20TA%20912%20and%20had%20stopped%20after%20crossing%20the%20nine%20signals%20awaiting%20fresh%20clearance%20to%20proceed%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EAuthorisation%20To%20Cross%20Red%20Signals%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Railway%20Board%20said%20that%20the%20driver%20of%20the%20goods%20train%20had%20been%20authorised%20to%20cross%20all%20red%20signals%20between%20Rangapani%20and%20Chattarhat%20railway%20stations%20due%20to%20the%20defective%20automatic%20signalling%20system.%20However%2C%20the%20train's%20speed%20exceeded%20the%20permissible%20limit%20set%20for%20such%20situations.%20The%20goods%20train%20driver%20was%20given%20a%20TA%20912%2C%20by%20the%20station%20master%20of%20Rangapani%2C%20permitting%20the%20train%20to%20pass%20nine%20red%20signals.%20This%20authorisation%20was%20crucial%20because%20the%20automatic%20signalling%20system%20had%20been%20malfunctioning%20since%205%3A50%20am%20on%20the%20day%20of%20the%20accident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F5076s2jg_kanchanjunga-train-accident-_625x300_18_June_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPhoto%20Credit%3A%20ANI%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20goods%20train%2C%20GFCJ%2C%20departed%20from%20Rangapani%20at%208%3A42%20am%20and%20collided%20with%20the%20stationary%20Kanchanjunga%20Express%20at%208%3A55%20am.%20The%20impact%20resulted%20in%20the%20derailment%20of%20the%20guard's%20coach%2C%20two%20parcel%20coaches%2C%20and%20a%20general%20seating%20coach%20of%20the%20passenger%20train.%20The%20driver%20of%20the%20goods%20train%2C%20who%20was%20among%20the%20dead%2C%20was%20found%20to%20have%20not%20followed%20the%20mandatory%20speed%20restrictions%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20crash.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20driver%20of%20the%20Kanchanjunga%20Express%20adhered%20to%20the%20safety%20norms%20required%20during%20a%20signalling%20defect.%20He%20stopped%20at%20all%20red%20signals%20for%20one%20minute%20and%20proceeded%20at%20a%20speed%20of%2010%20kmph.%20In%20contrast%2C%20the%20goods%20train's%20driver%20proceeded%20at%20higher%20than%20permissible%20limits%20and%20rammed%20the%20passenger%20train.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EAutomatic%20Signalling%20System%20Failure%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20TA%20912%20authority%20letter%20mentioned%20that%20the%20automatic%20signalling%20system%20had%20failed%20and%20authorised%20the%20driver%20to%20pass%20all%20automatic%20signals%20between%20Rangapani%20and%20Chattarhat%2C%20regardless%20of%20whether%20they%20were%20red%20or%20caution%20signals.%20The%20Railway%20Board%20said%20that%20under%20normal%20circumstances%2C%20a%20train%20encountering%20a%20red%20signal%20should%20stop%20for%20one%20minute%20during%20the%20day%20and%20two%20minutes%20at%20night%2C%20proceeding%20with%20extreme%20caution%20at%20speed%20not%20exceeding%2015%20kmph%20in%20good%20visibility%20conditions%20and%2010%20kmph%20in%20poor%20visibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fnvoveuhg_kanchanjunga-train-accident-_625x300_18_June_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20these%20regulations%2C%20the%20goods%20train%20exceeded%20the%20permissible%20speed%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20catastrophic%20collision.%20The%20exact%20speed%20at%20which%20the%20goods%20train%20was%20travelling%20has%20not%20been%20disclosed%20by%20the%20Railway%20Board.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERescue%20operations%20concluded%20by%20late%20afternoon%2C%20but%20efforts%20to%20clear%20the%20derailed%20coaches%20and%20restore%20rail%20services%20continued.%20The%20North%20Bengal%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital%20treated%20several%20injured%20passengers%2C%20with%2041%20remaining%20hospitalized%2C%20including%20nine%20in%20critical%20condition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EOfficial%20Response%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Commissioner%20of%20Railway%20Safety%20(CRS)%20initiated%20a%20probe%20into%20the%20cause%20of%20the%20accident.%20Railway%20Minister%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%20visited%20the%20site%2C%20overseeing%20relief%20operations%20and%20announcing%20compensation%20for%20the%20victims'%20families.%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20will%20be%20provided%20to%20the%20families%20of%20those%20who%20died%2C%20Rs%202.5%20lakh%20to%20the%20grievously%20injured%2C%20and%20Rs%2050%2C000%20to%20those%20with%20minor%20injuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20offered%20his%20condolences%20to%20the%20victims%20and%20prayed%20for%20the%20recovery%20of%20those%20who%20were%20injured.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F72486id8_kanchanjunga-train-accident-_625x300_18_June_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPhoto%20Credit%3A%20PTI%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20railway%20accident%20in%20West%20Bengal%20is%20saddening.%20Condolences%20to%20those%20who%20lost%20their%20loved%20ones.%20I%20pray%20that%20the%20injured%20recover%20at%20the%20earliest.%20Spoke%20to%20officials%20and%20took%20