r%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsocial-media-splintering-new-less-toxic-era-meta-bluesky-twitter-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esocial%20media%3C%2Fa%3E-related%20plea%2C%20issuing%20a%20surgeon%20general's%20advisory%20that%20urged%20Americans%20to%20pay%20attention%20to%20what%20he%20deemed%20a%20public%20health%20issue.%20Since%20then%2C%20Meta%20founder%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffacebook-mark-zuckerberg-senate-hearing-child-exploitation-social-media-law-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMark%20Zuckerberg%20has%20testified%3C%2Fa%3E%20before%20Congress%20about%20the%20company's%20child%20safety%20policies%2C%20and%20legislation%20focused%20on%20online%20safety%20for%20kids%20continues%20to%20work%20its%20way%20through%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20little%20has%20actually%20changed%2C%20Jordan%20said.%20And%20kids%20themselves%20are%20increasingly%20aware%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-tiktok-user-quit-mental-health-productivity-us-ban-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esocial%20media's%20potential%20harms%3C%2Fa%3E.%20According%20to%20one%20August%202022%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdigitalwellnesslab.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2FPulse-Survey_Adolescent-Attitudes-Effects-and-Experiences.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20almost%20half%20of%20all%20adolescents%20said%20social%20media%20makes%20them%20feel%20bad%20about%20their%20bodies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20warning%20label%20via%20a%20pop-up%20on%20an%20app%20isn't%20going%20to%20be%20the%20end-all-be-all%20to%20keeping%20kids%20safe%20online%2C%20but%20at%20least%20it%20starts%20the%20conversation%20and%20levels%20the%20playing%20field%2C%26quot%3B%20Jordan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226e85602f-a5ee-4e45-bb56-454ed7987179%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20mixed-bag%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EKaren%20North%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20digital%20and%20social%20media%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Southern%20California%2C%20is%20skeptical%20about%20whether%20a%20surgeon%20general's%20warning%20would%20do%20much%20of%20anything%20to%20curb%20kids'%20mental%20health%20woes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20far%20more%20complicated%20than%20putting%20a%20warning%20on%20something%20that%20is%20clearly%20dangerous%2C%20like%20cigarettes%20or%20alcohol%2C%20because%20social%20media%20is%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fmental-health%2Fhow-does-social-media-affect-teenagers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereal%20mixed%20bag%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20North%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20true%20double-edged%20sword.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20social%20media%20has%2C%20without%20question%2C%20negatively%20affected%20scores%20of%20children%2C%20many%20young%20people%20have%20also%20used%20the%20platforms%20to%20build%20community%2C%20befriending%20people%20they%20would%20never%20have%20had%20the%20chance%20to%20meet%20in%20%26quot%3Bthe%20real%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20North%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20questioned%20which%20platforms%20would%20be%20subject%20to%20the%20surgeon%20general's%20warning.%20Instagram%20and%20TikTok%2C%20certainly.%20But%20what%20about%20something%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fduolingo-tiktok-social-media-manager-shares-strategy-2021-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDuolingo%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%20And%20what%20exactly%20would%20the%20warning%20say%2C%20North%20wondered%2C%20noting%20that%20social%20media%20is%20rarely%20%3Cem%3Eexclusively%3C%2Fem%3E%20harmful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20a%20warning%20%E2%80%94%20which%20could%20only%20be%20implemented%20with%20Congress'%20approval%20%E2%80%94%20could%20have%20marginal%20benefits%20in%20keeping%20the%20conversation%20around%20mental%20health%20top%20of%20mind%2C%20North%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20there's%20something%20even%20more%20powerful%20in%20fighting%20social%20media's%20perils%2C%20online%20experts%20said%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftips-raising-gen-alpha-kids-social-media-ai-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EParenting%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2238ac7a50-5b7d-46b7-9ced-f2b700838c62%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EProactive%20parenting%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20most%20kids%2C%20social%20media%20use%20begins%20at%20home.%20Parents%20set%20the%20rules%2C%20purchase%20the%20smartphones%2C%20and%20model%20social%20media%20behavior.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20as%20parents%20and%20caregivers%20have%20to%20say%20no%20and%20delay%2C%26quot%3B%20Jordan%20said%2C%20echoing%20Murthy's%20call%20to%20restrict%20kids'%20social%20media%20use%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkids-should-be-banned-from-smartphones-until-13-french-report-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Euntil%20high%20school.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKids%20often%20point%20to%20feeling%20left%20out%20without%20smartphones%20or%20access%20to%20social%20media%2C%20said%20Jordan%2C%20who%20is%20a%20parent.%20She%20suggested%20parents%20resist%20the%20urge%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fditching-smartphone-healthier-living-dumb-phone-family-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebend%20to%20their%20children's%20will%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20instead%20encourage%20their%20kids%20to%20focus%20on%20spending%20time%20with%20their%20peers%20in%20the%20physical%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20about%20when%20social%20media%20facilitates%20connection%20in%20the%20physical%20world%3F%20North%2C%20who%20is%20also%20a%20parent%2C%20said%20when%20her%20daughter%20was%20in%20middle%20school%2C%20the%20tween's%20peers%20exclusively%20used%20Snapchat%20to%20make%20plans%20and%20organize%20meetups.%20Without%20the%20app%2C%20her%20daughter%20would%20have%20been%20left%20in%20the%20dark%20on%20social%20gatherings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSomeone%20once%20said%20you%20have%20to%20give%20your%20kids%20the%20tools%20for%20success%20in%20the%20world%20that%20you've%20placed%20them%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20restricting%20kids'%20access%20to%20social%20media%20entirely%2C%20North%20suggested%20parents%20take%20an%20active%20role%20in%20teaching%20their%20children%20how%20to%20use%20social%20media%20as%20safely%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20hand%20over%20social%20media%20to%20our%20kids%20at%20a%20young%20age%2C%20but%20we%20don't%20do%20the%20same%20thing%20with%20crossing%20the%20street%2C%26quot%3B%20North%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20take%20them%2C%20time%20after%20time%2C%20holding%20their%20hand%20and%20pointing%20to%20the%20stop%20sign.%20We%20tell%20them%20to%20look%20both%20ways.%20We%20go%20to%20great%20lengths%20to%20teach%20kids%20how%20to%20cross.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20same%20should%20go%20for%20using%20social%20media%2C%20she%20argued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BParents%20need%20to%20teach%20their%20kids%20how%20to%20cross%20the%20virtual%20street%2C%26quot%3B%20North%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAre%20you%20a%20parent%20who%20has%20struggled%20with%20your%20children's%20social%20media%20use%3F%20Have%20you%20restricted%20your%20kids'%20access%20to%20social%20media%20or%20taken%20a%20proactive%20approach%20to%20teaching%20them%20how%20to%20navigate%20the%20digital%20world%3F%20Email%20the%20reporter%20at%20esnodgrass%40businessinsider.com%20to%20share%20your%20social%20media%20stories.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsurgeon-generals-social-media-warning-parents-protect-kids-online-dangers-2024-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1718675669000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6670db1fed9a404d829e8f3b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%