ow%20bag%20is%20designed%20so%20that%20the%20mixture%20does%20not%20come%20into%20direct%20contact%20with%20the%20soil%20beneath%2C%20effectively%20preventing%20bacterial%20and%20fungal%20infections%20from%20spreading.%20Eyyo%20shares%20that%20this%20grow%20bag%20is%20patented%20and%20much%20more%20durable%20than%20standard%20ones%2C%20lasting%20at%20least%20six%20to%20seven%20years%2C%20and%20potentially%20even%20longer%20when%20used%20in%20home%20gardens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20bag%20is%20priced%20at%20Rs%20100.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20461px)%20100vw%2C%20461px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Feyyo-4-1718112692-461x1024.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22461%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20grow%20bags%20use%20a%20clever%20method%20of%20drip%20irrigation%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Feyyo-4-1718112692-461x1024.jpeg%20461w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Feyyo-4-1718112692-135x300.jpeg%20135w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Feyyo-4-1718112692-150x333.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Feyyo-4-1718112692.jpeg%20576w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-352684%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20grow%20bags%20use%20a%20clever%20method%20of%20drip%20irrigation.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20these%20grow%20bags%2C%20Eyyo%20has%20developed%20a%20UV%20sheet%20that%20can%20protect%20crops%20from%20harsh%20weather%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20being%20an%20innovative%20farmer%2C%20Eyyo%20is%20a%20generous%20teacher%20who%20loves%20to%20share%20his%20knowledge.%20Although%20he%20has%20reduced%20his%20farming%20activities%20with%20age%2C%20