%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERawla%20Bisalpur%20Homestay%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20duo%20decided%20to%20move%20closer%20to%20home%20and%20start%20convincing%20their%20parents.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20elder%20brother%2C%20an%20engineer%2C%20and%20I%20faced%20significant%20challenges%20convincing%20our%20parents.%20They%20were%20sceptical%20and%20worried%20that%20I%20was%20too%20young%20and%20that%20leaving%20a%20stable%20job%20would%20waste%20both%20time%20and%20money%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CTheir%20scepticism%20was%20also%20rooted%20in%20the%20belief%20that%20only%20large%20properties%2C%20like%20the%20grand%20%3Cem%3Ehavelis%20%3C%2Fem%3Ein%20Jaipur%20with%2050%20or%20100%20rooms%2C%20could%20attract%20guests.%20However%2C%20I%20was%20convinced%20that%20a%20smaller%2C%20more%20intimate%20setting%20would%20work%20just%20as%20well.%20After%20persistent%20persuasion%2C%20my%20father%20finally%20agreed%20during%20Diwali%20in%202017%2C%20offering%20to%20finance%20the%20project%20while%20leaving%20the%20execution%20up%20to%20me.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20several%20years%2C%20they%20remained%20deeply%20involved%20in%20the%20project%2C%20networking%20with%20individuals%20in%20the%20travel%20industry%20and%20inviting%20experts%20to%20provide%20feedback.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20began%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F335727%2Fintach-bengaluru-convenor-meera-iyer-restoring-forgotten-heritage-conservation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erestoration%20process%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20in%202019%2C%20we%20proudly%20opened%20our%20homestay%2C%20blending%20our%20rich%20heritage%20with%20modern%20hospitality%2C%20allowing%20visitors%20to%20experience%20the%20charm%20and%20history%20of%20our%20ancestral%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20restoration%2C%20the%20duo%20decided%20to%20maintain%20the%20original%20structure%20while%20enhancing%20the%20ground%20floor%2C%20which%20was%20previously%20unused.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20family%20continued%20living%20on%20the%20first%20floor%2C%20keeping%20our%20personal%20and%20guest%20spaces%20separate.%20The%20restoration%20aimed%20to%20preserve%20the%20original%20architecture%2C%20using%20local%20artisans%20without%20involving%20any%20architects%2C%20engineers%2C%20or%20designers%20due%20to%20the%20small%20and%20remote%20location%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20front%20fa%C3%A7ade%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Ehaveli%3C%2Fem%3E%20resembles%20a%20mud%20castle%20built%20from%20lime%2C%20mud%2C%20and%20bricks%20without%20any%20stonework.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20traditional%20construction%20method%20has%20a%20natural%20temperature-regulating%20effect%2C%20keeping%20the%20interiors%20warm%20in%20winter%20and%20cool%20in%20summer.%20We%20focused%20on%20restoring%20the%20flooring%20and%20ensuring%20the%20guests%E2%80%99%20comfort%20while%20preserving%20the%20historical%20essence%20of%20the%20place.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20problems%20he%20faced%20during%20the%20restoration%20work%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CRemoving%20the%20original%20big%20stones%20from%20the%20flooring%20was%20a%20difficult%20task.%20Additionally%2C%20restoring%20the%20area%20that%20used%20to%20serve%20as%20stables%20was%20particularly%20challenging%20due%20to%20its%20location%20at%20the%20base%20of%20a%20hill%2C%20which%20caused%20rainwater%20to%20flow%20naturally%20into%20the%20structure.%20We%20needed%20to%20restore%20the%20flooring%20in%20this%20area%20as%20well%2C%20ensuring%20it%20remained%20true%20to%20the%20original%20construction%20methods.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC6AkJzGydrz%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC6AkJzGydrz%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC6AkJzGydrz%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Rawla%20Bisalpur%20JAWAI%20(%40rawla_bisalpur)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFinding%20suitable%20stones%20and%20artisans%20capable%20of%20replicating%20the%20old%20techniques%20was%20tough.%20Fortunately%2C%20we%20found%20a%20villager%2C%20though%20he%20had%20issues%20with%20his%20knee%20and%20leg%2C%20who%20was%20experienced%20with%20stonework%20and%20helped%20us%20restore%20the%20flooring%20to%20its%20original%20condition.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EOf%20royals%20and%20royal%20stories%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERestoring%20the%20place%20to%20its%20original%20glory%20while%20keeping%20its%20soul%20intact%20was%20very%20important%20due%20to%20the%20rich%20history%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Ehaveli%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecounting%20the%20fascinating%20story%2C%20Paramveer%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20story%20dates%20back%20approximately%20500%20years%2C%20rooted%20in%20the%20state%20of%20Sirohi%2C%20which%20is%20around%2050%20km%20from%20my%20current%20home.%20My%20ancestors%20lived%20in%20that%20area%2C%20and%20in%20those%20times%2C%20it%20was%20common%20to%20leave%20one%E2%80%99s%20place%20and%20fight%20to%20secure%20and%20travel%20across%20lands%20on%20the%20Maharaja%E2%80%99s%20instructions.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20notable%20ancestor%20of%20Paramveer%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F94978%2Fudaipur-elderlycare-india-governmentsupport%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresided%20in%20Udaipur%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20near%20the%20picturesque%20Pichola%20Lake%2C%20on%20a%20hill%20known%20as%20Haridas%20Ji%20Ki%20Makri%E2%80%94%E2%80%99Malri%E2%80%99%20meaning%20a%20small%20hill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20lived%20there%20with%20his%20army.%20The%20Maharana%20of%20Udaipur%20had%20issues%20with%20a%20troublesome%20tribe%20in%20the%20area%20where%20we%20now%20live%2C%20in%20Bisalpur.%20This%20area%20was%20on%20the%20border%20between%20Jodhpur%20and%20Udaipur%20at%20that%20time.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Maharana%20instructed%20my%20ancestor%2C%20Rao%20Haridasi%2C%20to%20suppress%20these%20rivals.%20He%20successfully%20conquered%20the%20land%2C%20and%20in%201705%2C%20this%20territory%2C%20comprising%2024%20villages%2C%20was%20granted%20to%20my%20family%2C%20making%20us%20direct%20subjects%20of%20the%20Maharana.%20Since%20then%2C%20from%201705%20onwards%2C%20my%20family%20has%20resided%20in%20this%20area%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20construction%20of%20the%20property%20has%20evolved%20over%20generations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20look%20at%20the%20pictures%2C%20you%20will%20notice%20a%20distinctive%20white%20building%20with%20Indo-European%20architecture%2C%20built%20in%201938%